         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botanic Garden 28/4/71 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ In accordance with a resolution of the Trustees of the Royal Park, passed at a meeting held this day, I have the honor to inform you of the Trustees permiss...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.04.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Frederick<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Miles</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A345 Royal Park<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Trustees<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letter &amp; minute book, p. 50, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne Botanic Garden 28/4/71</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In accordance with a resolution of the Trustees of the Royal Park, passed at a meeting held this day, I have the honor to inform you of the Trustees permission that the Borough Council of Brunswick may enlarge the area of its cricket ground in the Royal Park by a width of 200 feet at a length of 800 feet on one side, and by a width of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>100' also at a length of 800'<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on an other side as indicated in the marginal sketch,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sketch not<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>copied<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in letter book.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but while the Trustees grant this concession with a view of seeing your plans for ealy<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>early?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>planting of the above indicated area carried out they sanction this enlargement of your cricket ground only on a distinct understanding that the fencing should be performed to entire satisfaction of the honorary Manager of the Park Alb Le Souef Esq., that the fences should always be kept in proper repair and the trees be satisfactorily attended to at all seasons<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The permission was revoked unless the proposed development<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was revised so that it<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>did not take in parts of a park road;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>see M to F. Miles, 8 July 1871.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>F. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hon Sec. Trust. Roy. Park</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">F.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>G. Miles Esq</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Town-clerk of Brunswick</p>
